--- In nbwrpg@yahoogroups.com, EmprzAnastazia@a... wrote:
> Maxima.. near the edge of the cliff, heard the communique. But.. 
unable to 
> obey her orders. 
> 
> She herself was a wreck. The damage too great to move.
> 
> Her optics watched as the Predacons retreated. Her optics watched 
Hydras. 
> But, she feared saying anything ... aloud. Softly, a whisper 
escaped... 
> "Hydras," as she laid there ready to black out once more. 
> 
> Her audio receptors could hear the last bits of battle as it ended. 
& not far 
> from her, she heard Rodimus. 
> 
> She laid there... & listened. Contemplating. Wondering if she would 
cease to 
> exist out here or not.

It would seem that 'or not' would be the case, as Flicker sees her 
there.  Transforming to best mode, he picks her up and flies toward 
Pred HQ as quick as he can.
